These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, cabbage, plum
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, march
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person eating cabbage and the person eating plum##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Food   | cabbage     | cucumber | plum |
| Birthday   | march  | july    | october      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
3 different games are played: whist, go, billiard
City: rome, hamburg, prague
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person eating kale is the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person playing go and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Game   | go     | billiard     | whist      |
| City   | prague  | hamburg | rome |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
3 different games are played: go, scrabble, bridge
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, badminton, cycling
1. the person playing go is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is between the person playing bridge and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the person eating kale##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Game           | bridge | go  | scrabble   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Sport           | cycling     | golf | badminton |

