.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, indian, australian
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, ebony, mauve
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the australian##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the indian and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| Nationality     | indian    | australian  | turkish |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Color   | mauve | purple     | ebony      |

