.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, prince, siglo
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, almond-milk
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the fan of gospel and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking 7up##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Cigar          | siglo    | bluemaster     | prince      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| Beverage           | 7up     | hot-chocolate       | almond-milk     |

