3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person traveling to paris is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person traveling to venice and the owner of the horse##2
4. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| City          | venice | new-york | paris    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | fantasy     | drama        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

