1. the australian is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person eating radish and the canadian##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the canadian is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking tea and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | soy-milk | tea |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Nationality     | dutch         | australian  | canadian       |

