The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, bridge-climbing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, basketball, skateboarding
3 different games are played: domino, go, bridge
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person drinking water##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | soy-milk      | water      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | bridge-climbing | chess      |
| Sport           | skateboarding | weightlifting     | basketball |
| Game   | go     | bridge          | domino       |

