There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, italian
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the italian##1
3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is cricket##2
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | milk     | hot-chocolate | coffee      |
| Sport         | soccer  | golf       | cricket |
| Transport   | bus   | van         | airplane     |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian    | italian     |

