.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, water
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, august, may
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, police-officer
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower, daisy
1. the person drinking water is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's birthday is in may##2
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the coach##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | sprite    | water          | hot-chocolate |
| Birthday          | may | august           | june        |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | coach         |
| Flower   | iris    | daisy    | bellflower      |

