3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
4. the person eating mango is the fan of d&b##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby       | singing | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Pet         | horse   | rat       | mouse        |
| Food       | artichoke | orange   | mango         |
| Music-Genre   | house    | soul     | d&b         |

