3. the person who growsbegonia is the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who growsazalea##1
5. the person driving the airplane is the person traveling to rome##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Flower   | begonia | azalea  | daffodil     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| City           | venice        | edinburgh   | rome  |
| Transport     | train      | ship   | airplane |

