.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, bridge, chess
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, sports, thriller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, salsa
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, trike
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the person playing chess is between the person playing monopoly and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Game           | bridge   | chess   | monopoly |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | salsa    |
| Transport           | motorbike | skateboard | trike    |

