The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, romance
House: victorian, townhouse, tower
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the tower house##1
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
3. the victorian house is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person watching comedy movies##2
4. the townhouse house is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking milk and the townhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Movie-Genre         | satire   | romance | comedy |
| House   | townhouse        | victorian       | tower      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

