.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, hiking
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, december
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the person driving the car##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person driving the car##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person driving the tram and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby        | magic-tricks      | writing | hiking |
| Birthday         | september     | december    | january        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 